{"tid":509663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿豪言今季必奪冠","createTime":"2017-12-25T14:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T05:40:30.000Z","uid":333,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2bdff802b12dbdef6ca5a946735035bc253a8c46","tid":509663,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4wIt%2FDyNivndORFNwZq2VxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9e282106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】大勇翼鋒穆罕默德沙拿豪言，今季一定可以為利物浦贏得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah）今季從羅馬加盟利物浦，立即以速度及入球征服了球迷的心，現時以15個入球，跟熱刺王牌前鋒哈利卡尼在英超射手榜並列首位；而且沙拿的入球率更勝卡尼，平均96分鐘就破網。<br />\n<br />\n數字如此亮麗，這名埃及國腳自然心雄：「我希望在這裡取得冠軍，我加盟就是為了奪標，為球會、為隊友、為球迷贏獎盃。我們每天都努力訓練，就是為了勝利，我肯定我們今季不會空手而回。」<br />\n<br />\n紅軍現時於英超以35分排第4位，落後榜首曼城20分之多，相信後上奪冠的機會微乎其微，而且英聯盃早於第3圈就被李斯特城踢出局，不過仍有歐聯及英足盃可爭。"},{"pid":"25bd4f5edcd4afbe78d02ae6e7c73f228d0bb512","tid":509663,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"歐聯皇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bc68a12504cdc6cff9e807b9fcaa37cac61cd6","tid":509663,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"7fd461c79cd393874799259fd17ccae89b83834b","tid":509663,"uid":131176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"英超挑戰盃已奪，夠鐘訓教"},{"pid":"20f2961f58279344e58f2d7af90cf96caeb222ba","tid":509663,"uid":26862,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"聯賽38場都對雲加件廢老就有可能嘅"},{"pid":"d8fad06de213783cb4e4bcfa9dd54e4514e0afd4","tid":509663,"uid":92714,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聯賽38場都對雲加件廢老就有可能嘅</blockquote><br />\n38分奪冠"},{"pid":"759d954f689e3cd307d307913923f7ded9cd7f16","tid":509663,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,